Slash commands (type in this chat):

Command	Does
/jodl-status	Read bus files → report sessions, task counts, stuck tasks, active events
/jodl-run	Print exact start-up commands for all three providers
/jodl-stop	Detach a provider — finds stuck claimed tasks, gives reclaim commands
/jodl-event	Walk through broadcasting a SYNAPSE event
Detach flow when done with a model:

Ctrl+C in that model's terminal (kills daemon)
Type /jodl-stop here → I find any claimed-<provider>-*.yaml still locked → give you the exact --force-reclaim commands to return them to pending
Other daemons pick up those tasks next poll — zero lost work
